data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome home to this beautiful home that is located in a gated community, has a full fenced in back yard and backs on to a nature reserve so you have no rear neighbors. The home greets you great curb appeal with a long driveway leading to your 2 car garage and your new front porch. Inside you can enjoy high ceilings with an open concept kitchen with lots of cabinet space and a large island allowing for a great entertaining area with it opening to your great room as well as a pass through to a formal living room. The split floor plan gives the oversized master bedroom a lot of privacy which has an attached bathroom with double vanities, soak-in tub, walk-in shower and a large walk-in closet. There are 3 other bedrooms that share the hall bathroom (pool bathroom) which leads out to your large screened in back lanai area where you can then access your oversized shed for extra storage. There is an indoor laundry room which then takes you out to your full 2 car attached garage. This home is a must see so schedule a private tour.
